[[["ccomp", "nsubj", "det", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "nsubj", "det", "amod", "appos", "nmod:poss", "det", "case", "nmod", "case"], "The moment I arrived in Lijiang, a big waterwheel, the town's landmark, came into view."], [["nsubj", "dobj", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "det", "case", "amod"], "It indicated the important role of water in the people's everyday lives."], [["nsubj", "det", "nmod", "case", "amod", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "cc", "conj", "nmod", "case", "amod", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "det"], "The water came from melted snow in the nearby mountains and turned into countless streams that flowed through the town."], [["nsubj", "det", "dobj", "det", "amod", "compound", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "nmod:poss", "det", "case", "amod"], "These streams formed a well-rounded canal system that supplied water for the people's daily needs."], [["nmod", "case", "det", "nsubj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod"], "On some streets, I found wells with a unique design."], [["nsubjpass", "det", "amod", "advmod", "auxpass", "compound:prt", "nmod", "case", "nummod", "amod"], "The so-called \"three-eyed\" well was made up of three linked pools."], [["nsubj", "det", "cop", "case", "det", "amod"], "Each pool was at a different level."], [["nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "nsubj", "ccomp", "nsubj", "det", "xcomp", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "cc", "conj"], "In the early morning, I saw a child take drinking water from the first and highest pool."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "nmod:poss", "amod", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod"], "Then his older sister washed food in the second pool."], [["nsubj", "nmod:poss", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "cc", "conj"], "His mother washed clothes in the last and lowest pool."], [["nsubj", "det", "dobj", "det", "amod", "cc", "conj", "nsubjpass", "det", "auxpass", "advmod", "cc", "conj", "nmod", "case", "amod"], "Each pool had a different purpose, and the water was used again and again at different levels."], [["nsubj", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "compound", "cop", "nmod:poss", "compound", "compound"], "Another admirable design of water use was their \"street cleaning\" system."], [["nsubjpass", "det", "auxpass", "nmod", "case", "det"], "The marketplace was built on a slope."], [["nsubj", "det", "nmod", "case", "det", "cc", "conj", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "det"], "A canal flowed along the west and the higher side of the slope."], [["advcl", "advmod", "nsubjpass", "nmod:poss", "det", "case", "auxpass", "nsubj", "det", "nmod", "case", "det", "cop"], "When a day's trade was done, the ground of the square was dirty."], [["nsubj", "det", "dobj", "det", "compound", "nmod", "case", "det", "advcl", "mark", "dobj", "compound", "nmod", "case", "det"], "The people closed a water gate on the canal to let water flow over the streets."], [["nsubj", "compound:prt", "dobj", "det", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det"], "Everyone picked up a brush and took part in the cleaning."], [["nsubj", "det", "amod", "advmod", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "appos", "det", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "det"], "The dirty water then flowed into a lower canal, a ditch, on the other side of the square."], [["nmod", "case", "nsubjpass", "auxpass", "compound:prt", "nmod", "case", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "det", "amod"], "From there, it was directed out of town to water the nearby farms."], [["nsubj", "advmod", "dobj", "det", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "det", "compound", "compound"], "I also got a brush and joined this \"street washing carnival.\""], [["nsubj", "ccomp", "nmod", "case", "det", "nmod", "case", "det"], "I saw smiles on the faces of the people."], [["nsubj", "det", "compound", "cop", "nmod", "case", "det", "acl:relcl", "nsubj"], "The Lijiang people were happy with the way they lived."], [["nsubj", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "nmod", "case"], "They cherished water as a gift from heaven."], [["nsubj", "dobj", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "det", "advcl", "mark", "mwe", "nsubj", "aux", "nmod", "case", "nmod", "case"], "They made the best use of this resource so that they could live in harmony with nature."]]